		</p>
		
	</header>
	
	
	<div class="content clearfix">
		<p>The Widgetkit Gallery provides smart and automated way to publish images on your website. You only need to select the image folders and the whole gallery is generated automatically.</p>

<h2>Features</h2>

<ul class="check">
	<li>Folder based image selection</li>
	<li>Automatic thumbnail creation</li>
	<li>Support for multiple image folders</li>
	<li>Uses the Widgetkit Slideshow and all its features</li>
	<li>Support for image captions</li>
	<li>Build with HTML5, CSS3, PHP 5.2+, and the latest jQuery version</li>
	<li>Works with Joomla 1.5, 1.6, WordPress and Stand-alone</li>
</ul>

<h2>Example</h2>


